      <title>美国债务可持续性现被视为最大的金融稳定风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/us-debt-sustainability-now-seen-as-top-financial-stability-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储的一项调查显示，美国政府的债务负担现在被视为金融稳定的最大风险，其风险超过了持续的通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/us-debt-sustainability-now-seen-as-top-financial-stability-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altas、Leonard Green 准备出售商业屋顶公司 Tecta America</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/altas-leonard-green-said-to-prepare-for-sale-of-tecta-america</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Tecta America Corp. 的私募股权所有者正在考虑这家商业屋顶公司的战略选择，包括出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/altas-leonard-green-said-to-prepare-for-sale-of-tecta-america</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 20:58:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Project Liberty：我们有能力收购 TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-22/project-liberty-we-re-in-a-position-to-buy-tiktok-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Project Liberty 创始人 Frank McCourt Jr. 表示，该公司可能有机会在“TikTok 被出售时”收购 TikTok。他与 Caroline Hyde 一起在“彭博科技”上进行讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
